@nastynate3163
I see it as fitting more because it has such a climactic feel to it.

You've endured through nineteen of the galaxy's most difficult tracks, and you're about to take on the most complex of them all: a dusty strip of pavement that snakes through the monuments of a massive magma-covered planetoid. One wrong move could cost you the win, or even your life. And yet, with the right maneuvers, you can pull in front of the pack and become the galaxy's greatest racing champion. Perfect.
